data.title: Pakistan cricket legend hunts for talent in Germany – DW – 08
data.meta_description: Cricketing legend Inzamam-Ul-Haq's Peshawar Zalmi is the first Pakistan Super League cricket franchise team to conduct a talent search in Europe this year. He believes the sport has a bright future on the continent.
data.text:
08/01/2022August 1, 2022

Cricketing legend Inzamam-Ul-Haq's Peshawar Zalmi is the first Pakistan Super League cricket franchise team to conduct a talent search in Europe this year. He believes the sport has a bright future on the continent.
